00:03:42.210 --> 00:03:43.100
It's pretty cool.

00:03:43.100 --> 00:03:44.060
ALAN SEALES: Really.

00:03:44.060 --> 00:03:44.560
[LAUGHTER]

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:46.476
BENJAMIN SCHEUER: I was
