00:03:46.476 --> 00:03:48.330
ALAN SEALES: So, um,
I mean you really

00:03:48.330 --> 00:03:49.613
learned-- that's all- like
everything in the show

00:03:49.613 --> 00:03:50.570
is a true story, right?

00:03:50.570 --> 00:03:53.028
BENJAMIN SCHEUER: It's a true
story, it's all a true story.

00:03:53.028 --> 00:03:56.514
ALAN SEALES: And so I'm going
to kind of give a synopsis here.

00:03:56.514 --> 00:03:57.930
So you learned to
play instruments

00:03:57.930 --> 00:04:00.762
from your dad growing up, the
